name: James Ward
description: I am a kind and caring man . I try to enjoy all moments of our life! I prefer to achieve my goals. And I will do my best always! My most desirable dream is to meet my woman. I cannot live without my special one. I am in my search now and I hope I will find you soon. I am dreaming to see the ocean and try lots of things! Have you ever jumped with a parachute? Let’s do it together! We can do everything we want. I just want to share everything with you.
